s, is a good thing.<br>
<br>
And if you still don't like it, you can remake a human or iksar or whatever smaller shadowknight, but when a nice troll/ogre shadowknight only necklace with Aura of Battle or Marvelous Visions drops, you'll probably just become envious again. *Poke*<br>
